ygData.msgSnippet: Ya and don t be picking on list newbies either! Welcome!! by the way! Go whine to that other guy who said 32k d about using jargon! I got enough small
ygData.messageBody:
Ya and don't be picking on list newbies either! "Welcome!! by the way!" Go
whine to that other guy who said "32k'd" about using jargon!

I got enough small bronze in the Torture Chamber room (first basement room)
of Unrest last nite to fully equip a char. Some times it just rains bronze!
Actually, I master ninja loot for our regular party (gods, I love saying
those words: regular party!) and gave it all to our cleric. Reagents are
not cheap you know!

Wanna hear something funny? A lev 36 enchanter was asking to join our party
and we kept saying "sorry - our stuff prolly too green for you and we are
doing just fine and NO we will not come camp the Ghost with you." Well
finally he stands there and says: "Unless you invite me and camp the ghost,
you are going to get a lot of trains on you." Hehe was this a threat or was
he just saying he needed our help? Hard to know when English is not always
the common tongue. Anyways, we were all lo 30's except our cleric who
dinged into 34. And we did see a bunch of trains! Which actually turned
out to be kinda nice way to fill in the dead spots between spawns (sorry, no
pun intended! <g>).

Sylly - the bard!
<Spirit of the Moon>
On Innoruuk Server

p.s. BIG THANKS!!! To Kalvidar - the super bard! He gave me a spare MM
drum! Woo Hoo! Big thanks to Lyly who gave it to him to pass on to a very
lucky bard - as it turns out: me!!!

p.s.s. MM = MistMoore - ok!
